zip archive.zip flname1 flname2
  compress & archive flname1 & flname2 as archive.zip

unzip archive.zip
  interactive unzip

unzip -v archive.zip
  view the archive without extracting it.

Note - if archive.zip exist then it will append or update, but won't override

options:
-r recursive compression
-l convert from LF to CR-LF
-ll convert from CR-LF to LF
